Open Racemenu (showracemenu in console), select Nord race. Press the preset tab in Racemenu and load preset "Ixum_JonSnow_ww"

Bodymod used in pics: [url=http://www.ladymoiraine.com/index.php?/files/]SAM[/url] with [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/59944/?]Ixum's Texture replacer
[/url]Skeleton used [url=http://www.loverslab.com/topic/25971-xp32-maximum-skeleton-extended/]XPSME[/url] (I use 3.13)

Installation:
Can be installed with NMM/MO, or manually
